WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.435
The classification of an Employee's position is

00:00:02.502 --> 00:00:05.672
significant because it ensures the Employee is properly

00:00:05.739 --> 00:00:10.377
compensated for his or her level of responsibility and work duties.

00:00:10.443 --> 00:00:13.279
The position must be classified, for example,

00:00:13.346 --> 00:00:16.249
to the proper occupational title.

00:00:16.316 --> 00:00:19.619
Article 20 explains options for Title 5 Bargaining Unit

00:00:19.686 --> 00:00:23.323
Employees who have concerns about the classification of

00:00:23.390 --> 00:00:24.190
their position.


